```

-and finally, the **watchPosition** method:

```js
public watchPosition(): Observable&lt;Geoposition&gt; {
        return Observable.create((observer: Observer&lt;Geoposition&gt;) =&gt; {
            this.gps.watchPosition(this.geoOptions).subscribe((response: any) =&gt; {
